Taylor’s thrilled when she meets Austin Riley, famed designer. She falls head over heels for him as he sweeps her off her feet and they begin a torrid affair, Her fairy tale ends when she’s confronted by Austin’s lover, Angelle. While she is still reeling from the news that Austin has been unfaithful to her, Angelle recognizes Taylor’s designs. She accuses Taylor of copying Austin’s designs. Soon they realize that Austin is using one of Taylor’s sexy models to photograph Taylor’s designs so he can steal them. Angelle and Taylor devise a plan for revenge.
